{"tid":2161350,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"XGU 傳統hell嘅仙制會否消失？","createTime":"2020-08-17T13:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T02:51:56.000Z","uid":237838,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"974f0667ad849373084e964c9e79703633dfe636","tid":2161350,"uid":237838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"今時唔同往日，以前日日要返學，自然多人爭campus hall。今年似乎返少d學，interhall com, Hello(hall-o)又似搞唔成，大家即刻狗衝哂二村，傳統hell想仙下人嘅都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜，仙制唔會因武肺而消失，只會冇咁仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相信大家經過今日嘅zoom hall tour之後會發現，有d hell冇想像中咁仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而某d仙過預期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有不少fm對開cam一事反應兩極，據說有人唔開cam比人quit左，有人開cam又比厹flirt...<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong><span class=\"gold\">如果你今日比人叫開cam,你...</span></strong></em><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"orange\"><strong>唔開</strong></span></span>cam比人quit左，恭喜你，唔洗再諗住呢間hall<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為你唔符合hall膠嘅preference<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算比你過到interview，入到hall你都未必住得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勉強冇幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你<span class=\"violet\"><span class=\"limegreen\"><strong>開左</strong></span></span>cam，恭喜你，你可能已經踏入服從仙制嘅第一步，人地叫你做乜你都做(當50%嘅人係呢類)，又或者咁講你對自己有自信係好事(當另外50%嘅人)，值得加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到有d fm比人quit左就喺度放負，真係睇到r哂頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有乜好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今屆好多fm話唔想chur，好多巴絲建議揀二村，二村多人揀，自然hall揀翻人，所以咪quit哂唔啱佢地(唔聽佢支笛)嘅人囉，咁都唔明？所以每間hell都有仙，只不過某hell可能仙d咁解，年年唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實XGU有龍華，唔鐘意hell culture唔該你去爭龍華啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好同人爭二村<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8bca5f7fa0c0accf5aa1f468c448d8f3928349","tid":2161350,"uid":237838,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-small\">Btw本身上講傳統hell仙制，講講下講左二村sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5ab7b7c0d168dbe5792628dffba791d37fa04744","tid":2161350,"uid":154634,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"仙制呢d垃圾藍血傳統一早應該滅絕<br />\n根本就完全同大學自由既風氣背道而馳"},{"pid":"ff2c4c016bd10a71f2d9afe946722fcaa508ffb7","tid":2161350,"uid":197563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:49:55.000Z","msg":"呵鳩屌你老母"},{"pid":"b487ba0b899c5c213dc8d609a1a1b801ae33245e","tid":2161350,"uid":330227,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"5ab7b7c0d168dbe5792628dffba791d37fa04744","tid":2161350,"uid":154634,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"仙制呢d垃圾藍血傳統一早應該滅絕<br />\n根本就完全同大學自由既風氣背道而馳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:14:08.000Z","msg":"到你做大仙嗰陣又唔係呢個講法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c717142b8d58046166d2395e041b24d64f62e0","tid":2161350,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"974f0667ad849373084e964c9e79703633dfe636","tid":2161350,"uid":237838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"